description: Decimal expansion of cube root of 10.
links: Harry J. Smith, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..20000
prog: (PARI) { default(realprecision, 20080); x=10^(1/3); for (n=1, 20000, d=floor(x); x=(x-d)*10; write("b010582.txt", n, " ", d)); } \\ _Harry J. Smith_, May 08 2009
crossrefs: Cf. A010240 = Continued fraction. - _Harry J. Smith_, May 08 2009
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_
extensions: Fixed my PARI program, had -n _Harry J. Smith_, May 19 2009
